@startuml Recruiter_Interviews

title Recruiter - Interviews (Module D)

actor Recruiter as "👔 Nhà Tuyển Dụng"

rectangle "INTERVIEWS" {
    usecase "Schedule\nInterview" as D9
    usecase "List\nInterviews" as D10
    usecase "View Interview\nDetails" as D11
    usecase "Update\nInterview" as D12
    usecase "Cancel\nInterview" as D13
    usecase "Reschedule\nInterview" as D14
}

Recruiter --> D10: 1. View interviews
D10 --> D11: 2. View details
D11 --> D12: 3. Update interview
D11 --> D13: 4. Cancel interview
D11 --> D14: 5. Reschedule
Recruiter --> D9: 6. Schedule interview

note right of D9
  **Priority:** P0 (Critical)
  **Status:** Need Validation
end note

@enduml
